  "title": "TransformData on Header Footer",
  "body": "Why can't I use TransformData on the header or footer?\r\nLike this:\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n            instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n                container: '#container',\r\n                attributeName: 'Attribute',\r\n                sortBy: ['name:asc'],\r\n                limit: 10,\r\n                operator: 'and',\r\n                transformData: function(data){\r\n                    data.myValue = \"some new value\";\r\n                },\r\n                templates: {\r\n                    header: \"{{myValue}}\"\r\n                }\r\n            })\r\n        );\r\n```",
